        "work": "1/3 = 4/12, 1/4 = 3/12",
        "explanation": "Rewrite both fractions with the common denominator 12."
      },
      {
        "subgoalLabel": "Add the fractions",
        "instruction": "Add: 4/12 + 3/12.",
        "work": "4/12 + 3/12 = 7/12",
        "explanation": "With matching denominators, add the numerators."
      },
      {
        "subgoalLabel": "Combine",
        "instruction": "Put the whole number and fraction together.",
        "work": "3 + 7/12 = 3 7/12",
        "explanation": "Since 7/12 < 1, no regrouping is needed. The answer is 3 7/12."
      }
    ]
